nodes.text: The JZ-5 Fusial Thrust Engine was a type of sublight engine that was developed and manufactured by Slayn & Korpil. Four JZ-5s were installed in the same company's B-wing starfighter, produced for the Alliance to Restore the Republic. Alternately, a single Quadex Kryomaster engine was used, its thrust directed through four individual ports. They were sometimes used for engines on Podracers.
